<p>On Thursday, Apple <a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2025/05/apple-reports-second-quarter-results/">reported its second-quarter 2025 fiscal results</a>. Revenue was $95.4 billion, up 5% versus the year-ago quarter. Mac revenue was up 7%, iPad revenue up 15%, iPhone revenue up 2%, and Services revenue up 12%. The Wearables/Home/Accessories category was down 5%.</p>
